title: Top 10 Quarterbacks in the NFL: Russ or Lamar at No. 2? Which future Hall of Famer doesn't make the cut? (Football 6/30)
description:
Rankings Week continues with an eye on the biggest focal point position in all of sports. Sean Wagner-McGough joins host Will Brinson to break down his list of the Top 10 quarterbacks in the NFL entering the 2020 season. A snub may surprise you, or may not, if you've listened to Sean before. Spoiler: Tom Brady makes the list, but maybe not where you'd anticipate. Could a newcomer like Kyler Murray crack the list? Dak Prescott or Deshaun Watson? Lamar Jackson or Russell Wilson? Sean settles the debates, or simply sparks them back up, on this episode!
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
